# Code Owners for Ranex Framework
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Security-related files require security team review
/docs/security/ @ranex-team/security
/.github/SECURITY.md @ranex-team/security
/.github/dependabot.yml @ranex-team/security

# Core Rust code requires core team review
/src/ @ranex-team/core
/Cargo.toml @ranex-team/core
/Cargo.lock @ranex-team/core

# Python bindings and CLI
/ranex/ @ranex-team/python
/pyproject.toml @ranex-team/python
/setup.py @ranex-team/python

# FastAPI application
/app/ @ranex-team/app

# Documentation
/docs/ @ranex-team/docs
/README.md @ranex-team/docs
/CHANGELOG.md @ranex-team/docs

# Examples and tests
/examples/ @ranex-team/examples
/tests/ @ranex-team/tests

# Build and release
/maturin.toml @ranex-team/core
/wheels/ @ranex-team/core
/bin/ @ranex-team/core

# Default owners for everything else
* @ranex-team/maintainers

